Handling other unhandled exceptions â€“ show you how to use the SQLCODE and SQLERRM functions to handle other unhandled exceptions.

set serveroutput on
declare 
enumber number:=&NUMBER;
en emp.ename%type;
begin
select ename into en from emp where eno=enumber;
dbms_output.put_line(en);
exception 
when no_data_found then
dbms_output.put_line('ERROR');
dbms_output.put_line('There is no such employee number');
end;
